forgiveBond(uint256).notice: Set bond as complete and forfeight future payments

getBond(uint256).notice: Interpret bond with given id into readable version

mintBond(bytes32,bytes32).notice: Append a new bond with given data

onERC1155Received(address,address,uint25.notice: SHOULD NOT be generally called by a direct user

onERC721Received(address,address,uint256.notice: SHOULD NOT be generally called by a direct user

serviceBond(uint256,address,uint256,byte.notice: Service a specific bond with generic currency

updateBeneficiary(uint256,address).notice: Update the beneficiary associated with a bond
